{
  "text": "\u2022 Web usage mining: It is the application of statistical and data mining methods to the Web log data resulting in a set of useful patterns that indicate users' navigational behavior. Rossi et. al. [CITATION_1] classify personalization adopting an Object-Oriented Hypermedia Design Method designcentered view on the structure and contents of the nodes and link topology. The classify personalization in the following ways:",
